name: Dancer 01
description:
A dancer stands on the beach pondering her next move. 

I find the moments between an action gripping. The pause, the sense of anticipation, and the self-talk that happens before an act fill a moment with palpable tension.  This feeling is what I hope to capture in this work. 

Made using Touchdesigner. Original music - made using field recordings and samples in Ableton.
